  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Events Promoter",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong><br />\nWe are a dynamic sales company committed to delivering memorable experiences and driving customer engagement through impactful events.</p><p><strong>Role Overview</strong><br />\nWe’re looking for an energetic and outgoing Sales Event Promoter to represent our brand at events, trade shows, and promotional activities. This role is perfect for someone who thrives in fast-paced environments, enjoys interacting with people, and has a knack for turning conversations into sales opportunities.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Promote products and services at events, exhibitions, and promotional campaigns.</li><li>Engage with potential customers, answer questions, and provide product demonstrations.</li><li>Distribute marketing materials and generate leads.</li><li>Collaborate with the sales and marketing team to maximize event impact.</li><li>Track and report on event performance, including customer feedback and sales outcomes.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in sales, promotions, or customer-facing roles preferred.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Strong presentation skills with a confident, approachable personality.</li><li>Ability to work flexible hours, including evenings and weekends.</li><li>Self-motivated, enthusiastic, and results-driven.</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive commission.</li><li>Opportunities to travel and participate in exciting events.</li><li>Training and support to help you succeed.</li><li>A fun, team-oriented environment with room for growth.</li></ul>",
